OL,3,CBaby found under floorboards could
OL,4,Chave lived 300 years ago, inquest told
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of a baby
OL,7,Fboy whose skeletal remains were found
OL,8,Funder floorboards by a construction
OL,9,Fworker has been told he could have
OL,10,Flived 300 years ago.
OL,12,FThe infant was discovered with twine
OL,13,Faround its neck and wrapped in
OL,14,Fnewspaper in an upstairs flat on Fore
OL,15,FBondgate, in Bishop Auckland, on 29
OL,16,FJuly 2024 and a police inquiry was
OL,17,Flaunched.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
