OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776355855
OL,3,CBaby found under floorboards could
OL,4,Chave lived 300 years ago, inquest told
OL,6,FAt an inquest opening in Crook, County
OL,7,FDurham, on Tuesday (14 April), senior
OL,8,Fcoroner Jeremy Chipperfield was told
OL,9,Fthat a postmortem examination could
OL,10,Fnot ascertain the cause of death.
OL,12,FDNA was unable to identify the infant
OL,13,Fbut did reveal that the baby was a boy.
OL,15,FOne type of radio-carbon dating
OL,16,Frevealed that the baby was born before
OL,17,Fthe first atomic bomb tests in New
OL,18,FMexico on June 16 1945, the inquest
OL,19,Fheard.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
