CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776355855
OL,3,CBaby found under floorboards could
OL,4,Chave lived 300 years ago, inquest told
OL,6,FIt was not possible to say whether the
OL,7,Fbaby was stillborn but Mr Chipperfield
OL,8,Fdid point out that twine was found
OL,9,Flooped three times around his neck.
OL,11,FThe inquest was told that police,
OL,12,FDurham County Council and a local
OL,13,Ffuneral directors have arranged a
OL,14,Ffuneral which will take place on 27
OL,15,FApril in Bishop Auckland.
OL,17,FMr Chipperfield released the remains
OL,18,Fto be buried and adjourned the inquest
OL,19,Fto be resumed on 18 May.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
